Europe regained the crown when the Danish team of Thomas Bjorn won the 14.5 points needed to beat the United States.
American star Phil Mickelson, who had to fight most of the way through the tournament, hit his tee shot into the water on the par-3 16th hole, admitting defeat to Francesco Molinari.
